Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE ABAN STYLE ULTIMATE TECHNIQUE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Lord Hadorra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My conversion to Superior Being\Nwas a rapid one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It put a strain on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I continue to fight,\NI won't last long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is beating Dai and his friends worth it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd gladly pay with my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know how powerful I can be\Nif I cast everything aside for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Power is a hollow glory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how strong,\Nthere's always someone stronger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dragon Knights, King Ban...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:03:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no idea just what level\NI can achieve.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd like to die as a more powerful\Nbeing than the Disciples of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to kill Aban,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but his students kept appearing\Nand threatening me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I merely killed Aban. I didn't defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't bear to die still losing to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You were born from Forbidden Magic.\NYou can't live if I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.64,0:03:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We are your pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Use us to fulfill your ambitions!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If it means dying for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I would gladly be shattered to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:04:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym.. your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is water coming out of my eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not human!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym... weeps?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Lord Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Fenbren?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder this place is called\Nthe Field of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry and find Chiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?! You better be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiu! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. So you all saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I found this for you. Be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I give everyone\Nthe new intel I've discovered,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,they will all be grateful to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Going to such lengths!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to totally chew you out\Nwhen we get home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He thinks we drove off his assailant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,From his wounds,\Nit was the bishop that attacked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, take Chiu and the others and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with these extra guys\NI can still take everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to base and see to their wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid! You may be strong but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it is, but be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on out!\NI know it's you hiding there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I completely hid my presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotten better, Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You were wise to send that Mage home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He lost his life once because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If he saw me,\Nhe might not be able to stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you come to settle things with Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep away from Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The humans are about to gather\Nall of their forces
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to attack Dark King Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai needs to be at their head!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm of the same opinion, Baran!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I chose to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll risk my life to prevent that fight\Nfrom ever happening again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You can risk your lives,\Nbut you cannot defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about any of you, even Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My objective is the Dark King himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark King Ban?!\NYou're here for his head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you no explanations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He cannot be allowed to live. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait Baran!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then our objectives are aligned!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us put the past behind us\Nand work together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You rescued Chiu, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,With you by our side,\Nour forces will be considerable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,For Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine! Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Over my dead body!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Dragon Master General Baran!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't insult me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The humans are also an enemy\Nthat must be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I would rather die than help them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I merely saved the little rat
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,because I stumbled on him while searching\Nfor an entrance to Ban's stronghold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I now know the entrance is underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They claim not even a Dragon Knight\Ncan penetrate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait Baran!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Go alone and the enemy\Nwill focus their attack on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll face Ban's minions\Nno matter how many hundred he sends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on is between\Nthe true Dragon Knight and the Dark King.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A battle beyond\Nyour imagination will unfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back if you want to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those eyes...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.93,0:09:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's not the same Baran I once knew!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be...?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Our base of operations\Nhas become a field hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We can still regroup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiu and the others are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been healed and are all asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if Hyunckel and Crocodine\Ncan just come back safely...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, how could you leave them behind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just that\Nhe got so serious all of sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would Hyunckel act like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let you go any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.99,0:10:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here to thrash you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:11:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I know... no, I finally realize\Nwhat you're really after!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You intend to throw away\Nyour life for Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a Dragon Knight can emerge from\Na fight with Dark King Ban unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not expecting to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't allow that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let you fight such a hopeless\Nbattle, even if it's for Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's for Dai, then wouldn't\Nletting me go be more beneficial?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go alone, you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't allow that to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I leave Master Baran\Nand Master Dino in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This Dark Armour Spear I wield...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,can't allow that to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Larhart?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You would try to dissuade me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'll just listen\Nand obey you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadly, my only choice is to defeat you\Nbefore Hadorra detects us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is that stance?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.95,0:12:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To cast aside his weapon\Nin the face of battle?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is he up to?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His Aura... is gone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:36.56,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BLOODY SUKURAIDO!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:41.57,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}NEEDLE THOUSAND{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel's Aura has completely vanished!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's like a still pond\Nwithout a single ripple.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You drop your weapon\Nwhile facing Baran?! Are you insane?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Crocodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it looks like Baran realizes\Njust how dangerous this skill really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't sense any Aura from Hyunckel!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Baran's begun quelling his own Aura!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now my Aura is the strongest one here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. This is a self-sacrificing move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-sacrificing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Unleashing a powerful attack creates\Nan opening for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You intend to allow that attack,\Nthereby forcing that opening,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,which you'll exploit with a counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When I read my master Aban's book, there\Nwas one skill I thought impossible for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fifteen years ago, when Aban fought\Nthe Dark Lord Hadorra,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he attained this technique.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Aban Style Ultimate Technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.07,0:13:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hollow Stance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hollow Stance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Against a powerful attack from an enemy,\Nin order to avoid a fatal blow,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,one must completely erase their Aura,\Nand ride out the force of the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But one cannot reach such a state\Nwith a weapon and intent to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So Aban chose to cast his sword aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! Have you given up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Aban...{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Strash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aban used the Hollow Stance\Nand Aban Strash.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By combining the ultimate passive\Nand active techniques, he defeated Hadorra.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I, on the other hand,\Nalways held my weapon for revenge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To cast it aside and force myself\Ninto such a hollow state...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,always seemed like pure absurdity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, Baran, this is probably\Nthe only skill that will have an effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Using the Hollow Stance, I'll create\Nan opening and use a counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.08,0:15:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The stronger the attack, the greater\Nthe opening the Hollow Stance creates!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For someone as overly powerful as Baran,\Nit's truly a terrifying skill!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why he tried\Nto suppress his own Aura to fight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown into\Na terrifying foe, Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to suppress my own Aura,\Nbut I can't erase it like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.73,0:15:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That state cannot be reached\Nwithout the strongest of resolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel? Who's he fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That man...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:16:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Baran's begun increasing his Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct. That's your only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll attack, but hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you endure my counter,\Nyou'll unleash your second attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, if you can endure my counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran means to put himself at risk too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, you've shown me your resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish, I shall face that skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes, Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Larhart, not a day goes by\Nthat I don't think about you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.84,0:16:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This attack will be the best I can do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should I fail to stop Baran,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you can laugh at my foolishness\Nfrom the afterlife.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon Master Baran?! That's him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:17:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Deserter of the Dark Army,\Nand Dai's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling when he'll turn\Nagainst Lord Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is perfect.\NWe can eliminate both of them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Albinass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They may be our enemy,\Nbut you can't interrupt a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows how angry Lord Hadorra will be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall take full responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All is for the sake of Lord Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All threats must be weeded out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Albinass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That wound...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder you like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What a terrifying warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Albinass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's no longer a threat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the one silver lining.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was you, Baran...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,who rescued me from that explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Hyunckel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He lives, but he'll never fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world could do this to him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In that instant,\Nthe Dark Army interrupted our fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was so focused on attacking Hyunckel\Nthat I couldn't do anything else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel and I would both have been\Ncaught off guard and died.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's when Hyunckel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Needle Thousand!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Bloody Sukuraido!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel used his Hollow Stance\Non the Dark Army instead...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}driving them off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:20:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All while knowing\Nhe'd take the full force of my attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,His words weren't just dull platitudes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He was willing to give his life\Nto save mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine, what must I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I ever repay this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It shames me Baran,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but deep down,\NI wanted you to fight Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it would benefit the humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured it was futile\Nto try to stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, Hyunckel still...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't deserve to say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He can be cold,\Nbut he's a man I'm proud to call a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just respect what he was trying to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Citadel, Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Citadel Gate lies underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiu did a good job in finding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I have to go there...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.98,0:21:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,while everyone is fighting\Nthe Hadorra Royal Guard on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a Dragon Knight\Ncan destroy the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous to go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You need someone to go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go. Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're our key player\Nagainst the Royal Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:12.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:18.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:23.92,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:29.84,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:35.68,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.85,0:22:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.85,0:22:41.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:47.44,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:53.45,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.62,0:22:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.62,0:22:59.25,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.42,0:23:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.42,0:23:01.88,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.04,0:23:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.04,0:23:05.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:10.30,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:16.72,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:22.65,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.81,0:23:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.81,0:23:25.36,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:30.11,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i0}
